column5: Allegheny National Forest ( my backyard) hosts some nice wildlife...  on my back deck  stumbled upon this..  we have these, too..    I participated in a " Rods for Troops" program...donated...this rod wound up aboard a US Navy ship    a few recent rods... match my truck  a few assorted grips  red/white/black grips & threadwrap to match    all for now..more after our week in your backyard..
awesome pics!!  Can't wait to see more...have fun
